{%- comment -%}
  Seym Editorial Showcase
  A pinned-scroll narrative for a single product.
  Left: sticky product image with subtle spotlight.
  Right: 4 scrolling chapters — each answers a question the buyer has.
  Closes with price + CTA.
{%- endcomment -%}

<style>
  /* ── Layout ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .seym-ed {
    background: #fafaf7;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .seym-ed__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: start;
    max-width: 180rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ── Left: sticky visual ─────────────────────────────────────── */
  .seym-ed__visual {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #f0ede8;
  }

  .seym-ed__img-wrap {
    position: relative;
    width: 78%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
  }

  .seym-ed__img-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  /* Gold spotlight behind the object — barely visible but present */
  .seym-ed__img-wrap::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -20%;
    background: radial-gradient(50% 50% at 50% 45%, rgba(201,169,110,0.12), transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* ── Annotation pins ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .seym-ed__pin {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 3;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateX(-6px);
    transition: opacity 600ms ease, transform 600ms ease;
  }
  .seym-ed__pin.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateX(0);
  }
  .seym-ed__pin--right {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
    transform: translateX(6px);
  }
  .seym-ed__pin--right.visible {
    transform: translateX(0);
  }

  .seym-ed__pin-dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #c9a96e;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(201,169,110,0.2);
  }

  .seym-ed__pin-line {
    width: 3.6rem;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(201,169,110,0.5);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .seym-ed__pin-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(13,13,13,0.55);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* ── Right: scrolling story ──────────────────────────────────── */
  .seym-ed__story {
    padding: 12rem 7rem 12rem 5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  /* ── Chapter ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .seym-ed__chapter {
    min-height: 85vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 6rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(13,13,13,0.07);
    opacity: 0.28;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 800ms cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1),
                transform 800ms cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1);
  }
  .seym-ed__chapter.active {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  .seym-ed__chapter:first-child {
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .seym-ed__chapter-num {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c9a96e;
    margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
  }

  .seym-ed__eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(13,13,13,0.38);
    margin-bottom: 2.4rem;
  }

  .seym-ed__heading {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 3.8vw, 5.4rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: 1.02;
    color: #0d0d0d;
    margin: 0 0 2.8rem 0;
    max-width: 22ch;
  }

  .seym-ed__body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.78;
    letter-spacing: 0.005em;
    color: rgba(13,13,13,0.6);
    max-width: 46ch;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .seym-ed__detail {
    margin-top: 3.2rem;
    padding: 2.4rem;
    background: #f0ede8;
    border-left: 2px solid #c9a96e;
  }

  .seym-ed__detail p {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: rgba(13,13,13,0.75);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  /* ── Acquire block ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .seym-ed__acquire {
    padding: 7rem 0 0 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(13,13,13,0.07);
  }

  .seym-ed__acquire-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.36em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(13,13,13,0.38);
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }

  .seym-ed__acquire-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 3.2vw, 4.4rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: #0d0d0d;
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem 0;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .seym-ed__acquire-price {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(13,13,13,0.45);
    margin: 0 0 3.6rem 0;
  }

  .seym-ed__acquire-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #fafaf7;
    background: #0d0d0d;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 1.8rem 4rem;
    border: 1px solid #0d0d0d;
    transition: background 600ms cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1),
                color 600ms cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1);
  }
  .seym-ed__acquire-btn:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: #0d0d0d;
  }

  .seym-ed__acquire-note {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1.6rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: rgba(13,13,13,0.35);
  }

  /* ── Responsive ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 989px) {
    .seym-ed__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .seym-ed__visual {
      position: relative;
      height: 65vw;
      min-height: 32rem;
    }
    .seym-ed__img-wrap {
      width: 64%;
      aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    }
    .seym-ed__story {
      padding: 6rem 2.4rem 8rem;
    }
    .seym-ed__chapter {
      min-height: auto;
      padding: 4rem 0;
      opacity: 1;
      transform: none;
    }
    .seym-ed__pin { display: none; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 749px) {
    .seym-ed__heading { font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 4.4rem); }
    .seym-ed__visual { height: 80vw; }
  }
</style>

{%- assign _prod_handle = section.settings.product | strip -%}
{%- if _prod_handle != blank -%}
  {%- assign product = all_products[_prod_handle] -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- if product == blank and section.settings.collection != blank -%}
  {%- assign product = collections[section.settings.collection].products.first -%}
{%- endif -%}

<section class="seym-ed" id="SeymEd-{{ section.id }}">
  <div class="seym-ed__inner">

    <!-- LEFT: Sticky product visual -->
    <div class="seym-ed__visual">
      <div class="seym-ed__img-wrap">
        {%- if product != blank and product.featured_image -%}
          <img
            src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
            alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | default: product.title | escape }}"
            loading="eager"
            width="900"
            height="1200"
          />
        {%- elsif section.settings.fallback_image -%}
          <img
            src="{{ section.settings.fallback_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
            alt="{{ section.settings.fallback_image.alt | escape }}"
            loading="eager"
            width="900"
            height="1200"
          />
        {%- else -%}
          {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'placeholder-svg' }}
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          {%- if block.type == 'pin' and block.settings.label != blank -%}
            <div
              class="seym-ed__pin{% if block.settings.side == 'right' %} seym-ed__pin--right{% endif %}"
              style="top:{{ block.settings.top }}%;left:{{ block.settings.left }}%;"
              data-pin="{{ forloop.index }}"
              {{ block.shopify_attributes }}
            >
              <span class="seym-ed__pin-dot"></span>
              <span class="seym-ed__pin-line"></span>
              <span class="seym-ed__pin-label">{{ block.settings.label }}</span>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT: Scrolling story -->
    <div class="seym-ed__story">

      {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
        {%- if block.type == 'chapter' -%}
          <div class="seym-ed__chapter" data-chapter="{{ forloop.index }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
            {%- if block.settings.chapter_num != blank -%}
              <span class="seym-ed__chapter-num">{{ block.settings.chapter_num }}</span>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if block.settings.eyebrow != blank -%}
              <span class="seym-ed__eyebrow">{{ block.settings.eyebrow }}</span>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if block.settings.heading != blank -%}
              <h2 class="seym-ed__heading">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if block.settings.body != blank -%}
              <p class="seym-ed__body">{{ block.settings.body }}</p>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if block.settings.pullquote != blank -%}
              <div class="seym-ed__detail">
                <p>{{ block.settings.pullquote }}</p>
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}

      <!-- Acquire -->
      <div class="seym-ed__acquire">
        <span class="seym-ed__acquire-eyebrow">{{ section.settings.acquire_eyebrow | default: 'Add to your collection' }}</span>
        {%- if product != blank -%}
          <h3 class="seym-ed__acquire-name">{{ product.title }}</h3>
          <p class="seym-ed__acquire-price">{{ product.price | money }}</p>
          <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="seym-ed__acquire-btn">{{ section.settings.cta_label | default: 'Acquire this piece' }}</a>
          {%- if section.settings.acquire_note != blank -%}
            <span class="seym-ed__acquire-note">{{ section.settings.acquire_note }}</span>
          {%- endif -%}
        {%- elsif section.settings.cta_link != blank -%}
          <a href="{{ section.settings.cta_link }}" class="seym-ed__acquire-btn">{{ section.settings.cta_label | default: 'Explore the collection' }}</a>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
(function () {
  var section = document.getElementById('SeymEd-{{ section.id }}');
  if (!section) return;

  var chapters = section.querySelectorAll('.seym-ed__chapter');
  var pins = section.querySelectorAll('.seym-ed__pin');

  if (window.matchMedia('(max-width: 989px)').matches) return;

  // Activate first chapter immediately
  if (chapters[0]) chapters[0].classList.add('active');

  var obs = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
    entries.forEach(function (entry) {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        entry.target.classList.add('active');
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.3, rootMargin: '0px 0px -10% 0px' });

  chapters.forEach(function (ch) { obs.observe(ch); });

  // Pins appear after a short delay once the section is in view
  var pinObs = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
    entries.forEach(function (entry) {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        setTimeout(function () {
          pins.forEach(function (p, i) {
            setTimeout(function () { p.classList.add('visible'); }, i * 200);
          });
        }, 400);
        pinObs.unobserve(entry.target);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.2 });

  if (section) pinObs.observe(section);
})();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Editorial Showcase",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "shopify-section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "product",
      "id": "product",
      "label": "Product (specific)"
    },
    {
      "type": "collection",
      "id": "collection",
      "label": "Collection (uses first product if no specific product set)"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "fallback_image",
      "label": "Fallback image (if no product selected)"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "acquire_eyebrow",
      "label": "Acquire eyebrow",
      "default": "Add to your collection"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cta_label",
      "label": "Button text",
      "default": "Acquire this piece"
    },
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "cta_link",
      "label": "Button link (if no product)"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "acquire_note",
      "label": "Note below button",
      "default": "Complimentary insured delivery within Türkiye"
    }
  ],
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "chapter",
      "name": "Chapter",
      "settings": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "chapter_num",
          "label": "Chapter number (e.g. I, II, III)",
          "default": "I"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "eyebrow",
          "label": "Eyebrow",
          "default": "Origin"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "heading",
          "label": "Heading",
          "default": "Born from breath and fire."
        },
        {
          "type": "textarea",
          "id": "body",
          "label": "Body text",
          "default": "Each piece begins as raw silica — sand, flux, lime — fed into a furnace at 1,200°C. A master glassblower gathers it on the end of an iron pipe and gives it the one thing a machine never can: breath."
        },
        {
          "type": "textarea",
          "id": "pullquote",
          "label": "Pull quote (optional)",
          "info": "A shorter, more poetic line shown in a highlighted block"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "pin",
      "name": "Annotation Pin",
      "settings": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "label",
          "label": "Pin label",
          "default": "Mouth-blown"
        },
        {
          "type": "range",
          "id": "top",
          "label": "Vertical position (%)",
          "min": 5,
          "max": 90,
          "step": 1,
          "default": 30
        },
        {
          "type": "range",
          "id": "left",
          "label": "Horizontal position (%)",
          "min": 5,
          "max": 90,
          "step": 1,
          "default": 15
        },
        {
          "type": "select",
          "id": "side",
          "label": "Label side",
          "options": [
            { "value": "left", "label": "Left" },
            { "value": "right", "label": "Right" }
          ],
          "default": "left"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Editorial Showcase",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "chapter",
          "settings": {
            "chapter_num": "I",
            "eyebrow": "Origin",
            "heading": "Born from breath and fire.",
            "body": "Each piece begins as raw silica — sand, flux, lime — fed into a furnace at 1,200°C. A master glassblower gathers it on the end of an iron pipe and gives it the one thing a machine never can: breath.",
            "pullquote": "No mould. No template. Only the lung capacity of a craftsman and thirty years of muscle memory."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "chapter",
          "settings": {
            "chapter_num": "II",
            "eyebrow": "Craft",
            "heading": "Our Çengelköy atelier has one rule: never the same twice.",
            "body": "Each object is shaped by hand in our Istanbul workshop. Temperature, gravity, the angle of the pipe — every variable is a decision. Imperfections are not corrected. They are the signature.",
            "pullquote": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "chapter",
          "settings": {
            "chapter_num": "III",
            "eyebrow": "Light",
            "heading": "Glass does not hold light. It transforms it.",
            "body": "At dawn, amber. At noon, crystalline. By candlelight, the colour deepens into something you cannot name. Seym pieces are designed to read differently in every hour of the day — they are not objects, they are instruments.",
            "pullquote": "Place it near a window. Watch it change the room."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "chapter",
          "settings": {
            "chapter_num": "IV",
            "eyebrow": "Presence",
            "heading": "This exact piece will never be made again.",
            "body": "We produce in limited editions of twelve — named, numbered, documented. When this series closes, it closes. What you acquire is not a product. It is a timestamp in molten glass.",
            "pullquote": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pin",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Mouth-blown",
            "top": 28,
            "left": 12,
            "side": "left"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pin",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Unique air inclusions",
            "top": 52,
            "left": 18,
            "side": "left"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pin",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Hand-finished rim",
